But as for me...

14
00:01:07,440 --> 00:01:08,880
I was born to...

15
00:01:09,440 --> 00:01:10,440
win!

16
00:01:17,760 --> 00:01:19,320
For as long as I can remember,

17
00:01:19,360 --> 00:01:20,960
- I've only had one dream.
- Hit it.

18
00:01:21,360 --> 00:01:22,040
Jump.

19
00:01:22,200 --> 00:01:22,720
Die.

20
00:01:23,560 --> 00:01:26,280
And that's to be the best gamer

21
00:01:26,560 --> 00:01:28,360
