82
00:05:48,760 --> 00:05:51,280
The love between
an ordinary person and a killer

83
00:05:51,480 --> 00:05:53,920
really touched my heart, guys.

84
00:05:56,640 --> 00:05:58,480
Anyway, I want to thank
the other five people

85
00:05:58,680 --> 00:06:00,160
