97
00:06:21,760 --> 00:06:22,480
Jeez!

98
00:06:22,520 --> 00:06:23,640
That's not it, man.

99
00:06:25,160 --> 00:06:27,000
The one who's about to die
isn't the guy in the game.

100
00:06:27,200 --> 00:06:28,280
