101
00:06:29,760 --> 00:06:30,800
Am I going to die?

102
00:06:33,640 --> 00:06:35,360
How is that even possible?

103
00:06:35,840 --> 00:06:38,160
Derya, I'm hunting you down,

104
00:06:38,200 --> 00:06:43,800
