136
00:08:20,640 --> 00:08:22,520
What am I supposed to do, then?

137
00:08:22,520 --> 00:08:24,080
Just throw a match or two
and let him win.

138
00:08:24,520 --> 00:08:25,440
Do I really have to do that?

139
00:08:25,480 --> 00:08:27,120
Or do you want him and his toxic fans

140
00:08:27,120 --> 00:08:28,680
