147
00:09:15,800 --> 00:09:16,480
Uh...

148
00:09:18,320 --> 00:09:19,120
It's Soh.

149
00:09:20,240 --> 00:09:21,320
Thought it was "Derpy."

150
00:09:21,680 --> 00:09:22,920
Based on your channel name.

151
00:09:23,520 --> 00:09:24,240
Oh...

152
00:09:25,280 --> 00:09:27,440
I named it after a gun in a game,

153
00:09:27,680 --> 00:09:29,080
Derya MK12.

154
00:09:30,960 --> 00:09:31,560
What a nerd.

155
00:09:31,600 --> 00:09:33,400
You play a lot of FPS games, P'Three.

156
00:09:33,440 --> 00:09:34,720
I figured you'd know that.

157
00:09:37,720 --> 00:09:38,560
How dare you!

158
00:09:43,600 --> 00:09:44,840
Derya MK...

159
00:09:45,680 --> 00:09:46,840
Hearing that name makes me hungry.

160
00:09:47,760 --> 00:09:49,600
