178
00:11:36,560 --> 00:11:37,680
I'm done with this.

179
00:11:37,760 --> 00:11:38,840
You damn bear!

180
00:11:40,120 --> 00:11:42,720
You think I, Thr33Gamer,
wouldn't notice...

181
00:11:43,040 --> 00:11:44,400
that you lost on purpose?

182
00:11:44,640 --> 00:11:46,480
- I didn't lose on purpose.
- Liar!

183
00:11:47,320 --> 00:11:48,200
I'm sorry.

184
00:11:48,240 --> 00:11:50,240
Fine, I admit it.
I let you win on purpose.

185
00:11:50,240 --> 00:11:51,440
I just wanted you
to get your pride back,

186
00:11:51,480 --> 00:11:53,440
and I was scared
of your fans coming for me.

187
00:11:53,480 --> 00:11:54,600
Get my pride back?

188
00:11:54,600 --> 00:11:56,200
Are you trying to
low-key call me trash,

189
00:11:56,240 --> 00:11:58,120
