so that I could win?

190
00:11:58,160 --> 00:11:59,360
I'm sorry, P'Three.

191
00:11:59,640 --> 00:12:01,200
I'll do whatever you want.

192
00:12:01,280 --> 00:12:02,160
Anything.

193
00:12:02,240 --> 00:12:03,840
