No!

211
00:12:47,600 --> 00:12:50,520
Sh*t, this salmon is so damn good.

212
00:12:50,680 --> 00:12:52,120
Thanks for the treat, Soh.

213
00:12:53,120 --> 00:12:54,600
Your beef with P'Three is over,

214
00:12:54,680 --> 00:12:56,720
