225
00:13:39,440 --> 00:13:41,000
- What? You were thinking about P'Three?
- What? You were thinking about P'Three?

226
00:13:45,560 --> 00:13:48,080
- Oh, look at you.
- I knew it.

227
00:13:48,200 --> 00:13:48,960
No.

228
00:13:49,840 --> 00:13:50,600
