263
00:15:20,640 --> 00:15:24,360
850405

264
00:15:24,520 --> 00:15:27,120
(Derpy Kid, why aren't you
answering my text?)

265
00:15:27,120 --> 00:15:28,360
(P'Three's here.)

266
00:15:28,440 --> 00:15:30,000
(You don't need to give me your time.)

267
00:15:30,000 --> 00:15:31,480
